author: Elvia Malagon
title: Man threatening suicide in South Austin prompts SWAT response
text:
Man threatening suicide in South Austin prompts SWAT response Man taken to hospital following SWAT response Elvia Malagon / Chicago Tribune 
Officers and members of the SWAT team responded late Monday to the South Austin neighborhood after a man threatened to commit suicide, police said.
